caption.p: Adipocyte metabolism. Adipocyte volume (pL) (A), photomicrograph (B), basal lipolysis (nmol/10 6cells) (C), isoproterenol-stimulated lipolysis (nmol/10 6 cells) (D), oleate incorporation into lipids (nmol/10 6 cells) (E), and acetate incorporation into lipids (F) (nmol/10 6 cells) of normal-fat diet (NFD; n = 16–6), high-fat diet (HFD; n = 22–9), and high-fat diet plus GbE supplementation (HFD+GbE; n = 26–10) groups. * p < 0.05 vs. NFD and # p < 0.05 vs. HFD (One-way ANOVA and Mann-Whitney test on acetate incorporation).
